---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'IMG Global in Panama', level: 2 },
  { id: 'why-img', text: 'Why IMG for Panama', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-details', text: 'Coverage Details', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Consider IMG', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in Panama', href: '/countries/panama/insurance' },
  { title: 'IMG Global Review', href: '/providers/img-global' },
  { title: 'IMG vs Cigna', href: '/compare/img-global-vs-cigna-global' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'price', header: 'Price (Age 55)' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Global Medical', coverage: 'Core international', price: '$180-280/mo' },
  { plan: 'Global Medical Plus', coverage: 'Enhanced coverage', price: '$250-350/mo' },
  { plan: 'Global Medical Platinum', coverage: 'Comprehensive', price: '$300-400/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="IMG Global Health Insurance in Panama"
  description="Guide to IMG Global international health insurance for expats in Panama. Flexible coverage options at competitive prices."
  headline="IMG Global in Panama"
  subheadline="Flexible international coverage at competitive prices. Good option for Panama expats seeking value and customization."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/panama-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get an IMG Quote"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/img-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">IMG Global in Panama</h2>
  <p>
    IMG (International Medical Group) offers international health insurance with a focus on flexibility and competitive pricing. For Panama expats, particularly those seeking customizable coverage at moderate costs, IMG provides attractive options.
  </p>
  <p>
    As a US-based insurer with strong international operations, IMG is well-suited for American expats who want coverage that works seamlessly when returning to the US.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$200-350</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Monthly (Age 55)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">Flexible</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Plan options</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">US-Based</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Company</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Get Your IMG Panama Quote"
    description="Flexible coverage at competitive prices."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/go/img-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="why-img">Why IMG for Panama</h2>

  <h3>Flexibility</h3>
  <p>
    IMG allows significant plan customization:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Multiple deductible options ($250 to $25,000)</li>
    <li>Various coverage limits ($1M to $8M)</li>
    <li>Area of coverage choices</li>
    <li>Optional add-ons for dental, vision, maternity</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Competitive Pricing</h3>
  <p>
    IMG typically offers lower premiums than premium competitors, making it attractive for budget-conscious expats:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>15-30% lower than Cigna/BUPA for similar coverage</li>
    <li>High-deductible options for even greater savings</li>
    <li>Good value for younger expats</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>US Coverage Included</h3>
  <p>
    Many IMG plans include US coverage by default, valuable for American retirees who visit family or may return for specialized care.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-3">Good for Working Expats</h3>
    <p class="text-blue-800">
      IMG's flexibility and pricing make it particularly suitable for younger, working expats in Panama who want solid coverage without premium prices. The customization options allow tailoring coverage to specific needs.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 italic">
    Prices for healthy 55-year-old with moderate deductible. Actual prices vary based on age, deductible selection, and coverage limits.
  </p>

  <h3>High-Deductible Strategy</h3>
  <p>
    Given Panama's reasonable healthcare costs, a high-deductible plan can make sense:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>$5,000 deductible:</strong> Significantly reduced premium</li>
    <li><strong>$10,000 deductible:</strong> Very affordable premium, catastrophic focus</li>
    <li>Pay out-of-pocket for routine care at Panama's reasonable prices</li>
    <li>Insurance kicks in for serious illness or injury</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="coverage-details">Coverage Details</h2>

  <h3>What's Covered</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Inpatient:</strong> Hospital stays, surgery, ICU</li>
    <li><strong>Outpatient:</strong> Doctor visits, specialists (most plans)</li>
    <li><strong>Emergency:</strong> Worldwide emergency coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Evacuation:</strong> Medical evacuation and repatriation</li>
    <li><strong>Prescription drugs:</strong> Covered under most plans</li>
    <li><strong>Mental health:</strong> Limited coverage available</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Optional Add-ons</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Dental coverage</li>
    <li>Vision coverage</li>
    <li>Maternity benefits</li>
    <li>Wellness programs</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Limitations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Pre-existing conditions: Subject to underwriting</li>
    <li>Mental health coverage: More limited than some competitors</li>
    <li>Chronic conditions: May have limitations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Consider IMG</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Good Fit</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>Budget-conscious expats</li>
        <li>Younger/healthier individuals</li>
        <li>Those who want customization</li>
        <li>US expats needing US coverage</li>
        <li>High-deductible strategy users</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">May Want Alternatives</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Those with complex pre-existing conditions</li>
        <li>Those prioritizing service over price</li>
        <li>Those needing extensive mental health coverage</li>
        <li>Older retirees (70+)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>Age Considerations</h3>
  <p>
    IMG accepts applicants up to age 74 for Global Medical plans. For Panama's retiree community:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Age 55:</strong> $200-350/month</li>
    <li><strong>Age 65:</strong> $350-500/month</li>
    <li><strong>Age 74:</strong> $500-700/month</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Pre-existing Conditions</h3>
  <p>
    IMG uses full medical underwriting, which means:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Pre-existing conditions may be excluded</li>
    <li>Some conditions may be covered with higher premium</li>
    <li>Healthier applicants get better rates</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare IMG Plans for Panama"
    description="Find flexible, affordable coverage."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/go/img-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Prices and coverage details are estimates. Get a personalized quote for accurate pricing based on your specific situation.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
